  "known_residual_risks": [
    "C2-R1 increases local-chat prompt/output budgets and adds honest metadata, but it does not guarantee complete model answers. response_truncated=false only means JarvisOS/local responder did not slice the returned response; the model or Ollama may still stop upstream.",
